snippet.title: I WANT TO BE POPULAR! - Game by Yeray Toledano
snippet.description:
This game was made for the Spain Game Devs (Jam II) in 2020 by Yeray Toledano. 

All the concept, Game Design, concept, pixel art and programation was made by Yeray Toledano: 
- Itch: https://yeraytoledano.itch.io/
- Twitter: https://twitter.com/YerayBunnyMoon

All the music and sound was made by Mateu Camps:
- Twitter: https://twitter.com/mateucamps
